'''Vice-Chair of Communications''' was the title held by [[Lo Vapeet]] in the [[InterGalactic Banking Clan/Legends|InterGalactic Banking Clan]]. He was also known as '''Communications Officer''', and liased with [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News]] and [[Shadowfeed/Legends|CIS Shadowfeed]] networks prior to and during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

